## 🚨 Problem 4: ChatbotPage.jsx — Reimplementing Your Chatbot

He created a new `ChatbotPage.jsx` (241 lines) that **duplicates** the logic from your `Chatbot.jsx` component into a standalone page:

- Copies your streaming logic, embedding service calls, and conversation history
- Adds a new `/chatbot` route in `App.jsx`
- The existing chatbot is a **floating widget** accessible from everywhere — this creates a second, standalone version

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This directly conflicts with the architectural decision to have the chatbot as a global floating widget, not a dedicated page.

